/TD>\n<TD style=\"COLOR: rgb(0,31,64); BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">Limit to value of contract</TD>\n<TD style=\"COLOR: rgb(0,31,64); BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255)\">Limit to value of contract</TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></DIV>', 'general', '', '', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, TRUE, 'liferay.com.1', 'Joe Bloggs', FALSE);
insert into JournalArticle (companyId, articleId, version, groupId, userId, userName, createDate, modifiedDate, title, content, type_, structureId, templateId, displayDate, approved, approvedByUserId, approvedByUserName, expired) values ('liferay.com', 'SERVICES-ONSITE-TRAINING', 1.0, '2', 'liferay.com.1', 'Joe Bloggs', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'Services Onsite Training', '<DIV>For your convenience and to maximize knowledge transfer to your staff, Liferay offers hands-on training held at your company\'s site. Liferay Training is tailored to fit your organization\'s unique needs and can last anywhere from three days to a few weeks. Topics include development of portlets according to the JSR-168 (Portlet API) specification, customization of Liferay, and deployment of Liferay in a production environment. <BR><BR>Customized training topics to meet your company\'s specific needs are available. Prior to the training sessions, you and a Liferay representative will discuss your training needs and the appropriate training days required.<BR><BR><SPAN style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">Onsite Training Advantages:</SPAN><BR><BR>\n<UL>\n<LI>Cost effective</LI>\n<LI>Fully customized topics</LI>\n<LI>No traveling cost for your staff</LI>\n<LI>Your staff receives maximum knowledge transfer because topics and Q&amp;A time are entirely focused on your company\'s needs</LI>\n<LI>Courses can be tailored to cover introductory to advanced levels</LI></UL><BR><STRONG>About the Instructors:</STRONG><BR><BR>All of the training that Liferay offers is taught by the people who developed Liferay Portal. Our instructors have extensive experience with different technologies used to build enterprise architectures. <BR><BR>For more information, please&nbsp;contact us at <A href=\"mailto:sales@liferay.com\">sales@liferay.com</A>.</DIV>', 'general', '', '', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, TRUE, 'liferay.com.1', 'Joe Bloggs', FALSE);
