ational public contest.  Košice Airport has also recently exceeded the record for the number of handled passengers. In January 2006 the TwoOne consortium has been recommended to the Slovak cabinet as the winner of a tender for 66-percent stakes in Bratislava and Košice airports. Investments in Košice airport should exceed €24 million by the end of 2015.\n<BR><BR>\n<SPAN style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">Challenge</SPAN><BR><BR>Košice Airport management was primarily seeking a new attractive web site. But after seeing the power a web portal delivers in connectivity between the Internet and the company Intranet, the management instantly changed their minds. Although the project was limited by a modest budget, the Airport managed to gain a sufficient grant from the Ministry of transportation, posts, and telecommunications. The basic requirements included a user friendly environment, ease in administration, display of up-to-date information (e.g. arrivals and departures, weather, statistics, etc.), and a modern design. Košice Airport hoped to get an attractive Internet presentation and effective intranet system, both connected in an interactive application.</DIV>\n<DIV><BR><SPAN style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">Resolution</SPAN><BR><BR>The delivery of a custom portal system exceeded the expectations of Košice Airport. Many services were provided building on top of the Liferay Portal:<BR></DIV>\n<UL>\n<LI>Layout of tree structures<BR></LI>\n<LI>Full screen resolution layout</LI>\n<LI>Improved Journal portlet</LI>\n<UL>\n<LI>Full support of UTF8 for templates and structures</LI>\n<LI>Managing article discussions</LI>\n<LI>Counters for most read or discussed articles</LI>\n<LI>Assigning articles various categories for layouts</LI>\n<LI>Image thumbnails for articles</LI>\n<LI>Journal article with embedded Flash animations</LI>\n<LI>Access to remote services using a proxy</LI>\n<LI>Real-time display of arrivals/departures from external systems</LI>\n<LI>English version</LI>\n</UL></UL><DIV>Coming soon:<BR></DIV>\n<UL>\n<LI>Airport statistics</LI>\n</UL>]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-thumbnail-1\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-KOSICE-AIRPORT.screenshot-thumbnail-1.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-full-1\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-KOSICE-AIRPORT.screenshot-full-1.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-thumbnail-2\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-KOSICE-AIRPORT.screenshot-thumbnail-2.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-full-2\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-KOSICE-AIRPORT.screenshot-full-2.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-thumbnail-3\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-KOSICE-AIRPORT.screenshot-thumbnail-3.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-full-3\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-KOSICE-AIRPORT.screenshot-full-3.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-thumbnail-4\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-KOSICE-AIRPORT.screenshot-thumbnail-4.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-full-4\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-KOSICE-AIRPORT.screenshot-full-4.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element