 of the services that it offered in all the Telecentros offices in Spain.\n<br/><br/>\nHaving over 3,000,000 potential users, the portal needed to also connect all of the Telecentros offices.  Achieving this was important in providng communication and collaboration tools for its users.  Another important challenge was that all the tools needed to be easy to use -- many of these citizens have very little or no experience with a computer, let alone the World Wide Web.\n<br/><br/>\n<b>Resolution</b><br/><br/>\nGerminus developed the Telecentros portal using Liferay Portal. They found that the Liferay Portal had a user-friendly design.  It was powerful in connecting users yet simple enough for those who had little or no experience with the Internet.  Liferay Portal exceeded the requirements of the client.]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-thumbnail-1\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-TELECENTROS.screenshot-thumbnail-1.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-full-1\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-TELECENTROS.screenshot-full-1.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-thumbnail-2\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-TELECENTROS.screenshot-thumbnail-2.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-full-2\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-TELECENTROS.screenshot-full-2.jpg]]></dynamic-content> \n  </dynamic-element>  \n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-thumbnail-3\" type=\"text\"> \n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[content.liferay.com/4.0.0/images/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-TELECENTROS.screenshot-thumbnail-3.jpg]]></dynamic-conte